      <body>The consensus seems to be that it seems more like a shortcut for updates_attributes!, e.g:

@@@ ruby
  def foo!(value)
    update_attributes!(:foo =&gt; value)
  end
@@@

Thanks for the suggestion though.</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The consensus seems to be that it seems more like a shortcut for
updates_attributes!, e.g:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
&lt;code class=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;  def foo!(value)
    update_attributes!(:foo =&amp;gt; value)
  end&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the suggestion though.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
